      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTAwMWJjNGJiNzE1OTBjMzU4MWIzLnBuZz93aWR0aD0zMTUwJmhlaWdodD0xNDg4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e001bc4bb71590c3581b3.png?width=3150&amp;height=1488\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e001bc4bb71590c3581b3.png?width=3150&amp;height=1488\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e001bc4bb71590c3581b3.png?width=3150&amp;height=1488\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n答案是金錢 金主股東不單止可以監督 更可以直接操控媒體控制輿論 所以要監督媒體根本上要用錢包來投票\t\t</div>",
